function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	--Play Boss Victory Stinger
	Hydra.MusicOverride("DGN_Frac_MercysReach", "Music_Boss_Skeleton_Victory")

	--Wait for Stinger to resolve and Reset Dungeon Music
	Hydra.Wait(10)
	Hydra.ClearMusicOverride("DGN_Frac_MercysReach")

end
